                "text": "### This Item may contain spoilers from the Extinction Curse Adventure Path\n\nAlthough appearing as a multicolored piece of stick candy, this figurine bears a narrow snake head at one end and is as durable as stone. When activated, it becomes a rainbow-striped ball python except it lacks the Stealth skill. The snake can be used once per day, and it can remain in snake form for up to 20 minutes.",
