                "text": "### This Item may contain spoilers from the Blood Lords Adventure Path\n\nThis small toy fox has tufted, fluffy ears and buttons for eyes. When activated, it transforms into a big fox with the statistics of a riding dog. The stuffed fox always allows you to ride it. While you do, you don't take the \u20132 penalty to Reflex saves while being mounted, and its jaws Strike gains Knockdown. The stuffed fox can be activated once a day and remains in its form for up to 1 hour.",
